Replace the following lines:-

And if we wanted only the expression field itself to use the Thai font, we’d use:

What is <div class=mystyle1>{{Expression}}</div>?

{{Notes}}

Replace with:-

And if we wanted only the expression field itself to use the Thai font, we’d use:

What is <span class=mystyle1>{{Expression}}</span>?

{{Notes}}

Explanation: Use span instead of div for inline formatting. Div creates a separate paragraph.
